-- GQ Russia Chief Joins Prokhorov’s Media Unit, Publisher of Snob
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-01-10T08:32:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-10/gq-russia-chief-joins-prokhorov-s-media-unit-publisher-of-snob.html
GQ Russia’s Editor-in-Chief Nikolai
Uskov quit the company to head billionaire  Mikhail Prokhorov ’s
Jivi! Media Group, publisher of Snob magazine.  Novelist Michael Idov will succeed Uskov at GQ, according
to a statement released today by Condé Nast Russia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
